[We are very grateful to Dr Bellaiche for the immediate, detailed, and candid clarification, addressing ProMED-mail's RFI; exemplary transparency.

Israel's Newcastle disease situation has been a matter of concern for some time. Follow-up report No 14, submitted to the OIE on 15 Apr 2012, is available at http://web.oie.int/wahis/public.php?page=single_report&pop=1&reportid=11860. In this regard, subscribers are referred to the commentary on ProMED-mail posting 20120104.0028. - Mod.AS]
